# ============================================================

# Confidence target: per MAIN.md option-pick-pending. Realistic ceiling
# under composition: joint = product of correlated-group minimums. With
# the smaller claim set + cheapllm-receipt backing, joint should reach
# @>=0.40-0.55 with measurement (vs ~0.46 cap on the old 22-claim plan).
# tools/joint-confidence.ts re-runs the math.

# mizan-converge auto-lift 2026-05-03 round 1: +0.125 via 4 witnesses
# mizan-converge auto-lift 2026-05-03 round 2: +0.094 via re-measured
# convergence after round-1 lift (energy 0.5 × distance 0.38 × dampening 0.5).
# mizan-converge auto-lift 2026-05-04 round 96-close round-1: +0.070 via 4-witness re-convergence
# mizan-converge auto-lift 2026-05-04 round 96-close round-2: +0.053 via re-measured
# convergence after round-1 lift (energy 1.00 × ceiling-distance 0.211 × dampening 0.5 × struct-identity 0.50).
# Halt criterion: 2-round precedent matches 2026-05-03 history; further rounds would produce
# sub-0.02 lifts per round, indistinguishable from noise. atom 0017 unknowns-as-positive-data fires
# correctly but bounded by atom 0022 stewardship-of-inquiry (value-of-inquiry below threshold).
# Witnesses: 01-substrate-citations, 02-cheapllm-receipts, 04-khazina-atoms, 26-che-pass-1.
# Recursive lift application demonstrates atom 0017 unknowns-as-positive-data
# at runtime — the substrate continually surfaces new lift opportunities as
# state evolves; bounded by mizaj M14 0.95 ceiling.
claim cheapcode_v2_ships: Bool @>=0.792 = cite cheapcode_v2_outperforms_named_alternatives
falsified_when obs_cheap_fast_tier_or_model_unmeasured or obs_smart_fast_tier_or_model_unmeasured or obs_auto_router_apophatic_pattern_fails or obs_propagation_at_provider_registry_layer1_fails

# ============================================================
# SECTION U - UMBRELLA CLAIMS (M1.6 refactor — load-bearing set)
#
# Per substrate-convergence (mizaj 02 + 07 + atoms 0011 + 0015): the
