  proves True
  by audit cheapcode-substrate-runtime-validation-m3-19

# Discharge claim — atom 0016 runtime status post-M3.19 probe.
# Pre-M3.19: @>=0.40 (research-grounded structural fit).
# Post-M3.19: @>=0.65 (small-N validated; full validation requires N≥20 +
# novel negation tasks; sahih on positive subset still untested).
