#
# Path forward per atom 0011: the SDE is unchanged. 5 SWE-bench Verified
# tasks where codex+gpt-5.5 FAILS, dispatched through cheapcode-witness
# v1x at diagnose-the-fix level. PASS = ≥3/5 better diagnoses.
# Cost ~$0.73, wall ~45 min.
# ============================================================

