# M3.35 cycle 5 lift 0.78 → 0.85: M3.32 (code-witness), M3.33 (reality-
# check), M3.34 (conversion-factors) are THREE additional concrete
# instances of substrate-primitive-as-fork-side-runtime-critic, each
# M18-disciplined with burhan claims FIRST + tests FIRST + ~100% coverage.
# Each instance materializes one or more of the 5 axes:
#   - code-witness: enhance context (atom 0010), reduce hallucinations
#     (atom 0015), improve innovation (atom 0017 cycle output)
#   - reality-check: solidify ethics (mizaj 01 falsifier-first applied
#     to time/cost claims), reduce hallucinations (atom 0015 firing on
#     memory-based claims)
#   - conversion-factors: improve innovation (atom 0017 cycle on
#     conversion-factor table itself), enhance context (multi-dim
#     filtering surfaces context-specific estimates)
# These three are M18-validated implementations of axes 1, 2, 4, 5 (axis
# 3 — knowledge synthesis — was already validated by M3.28 v1x).
