# HEADLINE TARGET CLAIMS — the operator-set goal axes
# (M3.30 corrected confidences: gated on closing M3.15 + wiring v1x into
# auto-tier dispatch within the inherited opencode harness, NOT on building
# a harness from scratch.)

# Headline-1: SWE-bench Verified completion ≥82.0%.
# M3.29: @0.20 (assumed harness gap was multi-week build).
# M3.30 CORRECTION: @0.35 — opencode harness inherited; DeepSeek V4 Pro
# at 80.6% single-pass; substrate enhancements (atom 0010 cross-witness,
# v1x panel-of-experts on hard sub-tasks, atom 0015 hallucination check)
# applied at agent-loop decision points should plausibly close the 1.4pp
