# M3.29: @0.45. M3.30 CORRECTION: @0.60 — opencode loop already has
# multi-step dispatch; cheap-tier routing for routine sub-tasks within
# the existing loop is the natural advantage. Routing rule 11 already
# routes hard-reasoning to voter (cheap × 2 first). Codex burns gpt-5.5
# throughout; cheapcode-fork would burn cheap-tier on majority of sub-tasks.
