# ============================================================
#
# Per bcmea + atom 0011 (smallest-distinguishing-experiment) + atom 0007
# (anti-fab requires measurement not assertion), the load-bearing
# best-next-step is M3.43 + M3.44 RUN AS A PAIR for $1.30 total.
