# Composed cost envelope and confidence ceiling
# ============================================================
#
# Phase I: $43-138, mid $70-90
# Phase II: $20-60 inference + 1-3 weeks engineering
# Phase III: $43-138, mid $70-90
# TOTAL DOLLARS: $106-336, mid $160-240
# TOTAL ENGINEERING: 1-3 weeks
